  "status": "active",
  "description": "Roostless fixer and information broker; insurance is her religion.",
  "narrative": "Spindles-born, two-part name, which by Spindles reckoning means she is honest about what she is. Brell brokers everything: passage, papers, silence, and - crucially - she holds the insurance copy of the Marrower Combine's real sink-rate numbers for Hollow Vesse. She does not know yet what they are worth. GM ARC: the Combine's endgame breaks open when her copy goes public at exactly the right moment; until then every faction in the campaign has a reason to buy, befriend, or bury her. She survives by being more useful alive to everyone. Rumor 4 (the commissioned glider) is true: she is planning her own exit.",
